-------------------------------------------------------------

HOW TO USE

1. Build the project using build.sh
2. Run ./main.o PARAM_FILE

-------------------------------------------------------------

HOW TO WRITE PARAMETER FILES

1. Put in the following parameter names and values delimited with colon(:)
   - dataset : string -- main.o will try to find the datafiles in data/dataset
   - useDT : int -- whether to use the dependency tree structure(1 or 0)
   - lambda : double -- penalisation term for the phrasal length
   - datasize
useDT:0
lambda:0.5
maxLength:3
dataSize:0
useSent:0
useSWN:0
sigma1:5
sigma2:1
useCoSim:1
